  <name>Memento</name>
  <summary>Track movies you watch</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Memento helps you keep a personal movie diary. Search for movies, add them to your
      watchlist, and record plays when you watch them.
    </p>
    <p>The app includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>A searchable watchlist with sorting and pagination</li>
      <li>Play history with filters and quick navigation</li>
      <li>Dashboard cards for recent activity and top people stats</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

